<D>__{i'm checking in a special guest...}
<P>__{(obviously conspiratorial)}
<D>__{... miss enomis.}
<A>__{the concierge straightens as he recognizes viktor from a copy of "variety". headline: "taransky rides ingenue's coat tails to three picture deal".}
<C>__{concierge}
<D>__{miss enomis, yes.}
<C>__{viktor}
<D>__{miss enomis demands her privacy. you will switch off all surveillance cameras. i will escort miss enomis to her room alone via the rear exit. she will require no help with her luggage. she does not wish to be disturbed at any time for any reason. she will be departing for a function tonight at eight sharp.}
<P>__{(tipping him with a hundred dollar bill)}
<D>__{i'm sure i can rely on your discretion. do you understand?}
<C>__{concierge}
<P>__{(passing the key to viktor)}
<D>__{oh, i understand.}
